data.description: GOLF COURSE VIEW Discover this unique home in the Groves Golf & Country Club, a much sought after 55+ community. This charming 2 bedroom/2 bathroom/2 car garage home is situated on a large lot with stunning golf course view of the 1st TEE and just down the block from the Clubhouse located on a cul-de-sac.  A screen enclosed front porch leads to the front entrance.  The large eat-in kitchen has granite countertops and tons of cabinets. Large windows bring the Florida sunshine into the large living room which opens to screen enclosed lanai. Patio furniture stays!  Formal dining or flex space. Laminate floors throughout the home with plank travertine in the bathrooms. New hurricane rated double pane windows and sliding door. Outside of home newly painted 2023.  New hurricane rated garage door in 2023. New roof in 2019. HOA fee pays for roof replacement every 17-20 years, outside painting every 7-10 years, Cable TV/Internet, lawn mowing, and onsite management.  The Groves is a vibrant community offering 18-hole golf course, fully stocked pro shop, heated (in the winter) salted pool, spa, tennis, pickle ball, bocce, beautiful clubhouse with restaurant, ballroom, library/media center, exercise room, art room and card room.  Clubhouse with restaurant/bar offers indoor activities such as Trivia Karaoke and line dancing. Active Social Club brings a wide array of monthly activities such as Bingo, Pancake Breakfast and theme events. Enjoy all the conservation areas, dog parks, butterfly park, fishing hole, community garden and more. Take your golf cart to Publix, restaurants, bank, beauty salon and more. Land O Lakes is a growing community with many new shops and restaurants and medical facilities. Just North of Tampa, central to beaches, amusement parks and Tampa International Airport.
